         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">4/10/82 ¶  ¶ In reference to the original authority, dear Mr Wilson, given by the hon. the Chief Secretary, for the printing of my statistical volume on Australian plants, ¶ That is, M'sCensus, B83.03...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">82.10.04</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Thomas Wilson</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">X82/9373, unit 1409, VPRS 3991/P inward registered correspondence, VA 475 Chief Secretary's Department, Public Record Office, Victoria.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">4/10/82</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>In reference to the original authority, dear Mr Wilson, given by the hon. the Chief Secretary, for the printing of my statistical volume on Australian plants,<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>That is, M's<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">Census</seg>, B83.03.04; see<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>M to J. Grant, 29 October 1881.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>it may be of use to send back to you the enclosed memorandum, as the original letter, on which Mr Grants approval was noted, may not yet<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>[have]<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn1" n="2">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="background-color: #FFFF00; ">Word obscured by binding</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="background-color: #FFFF00; ">, here and below</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="background-color: #FFFF00; ">?</seg>
                     </p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>turned up again,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>I have forwarded now some accounts, which meanwhile had been held back</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Regardfully</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>your</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">Memorandum</hi>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>[After] due enquiry at three [tr]ading printing-establishments it was found, that the price at Mess. M'Carron, Bird &amp; Co's was the lowest,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="background-color: #FFFF00; ">[th]e firm declining to tender</seg>
               <seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="background-color: #FFFF00; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn2" n="3">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; margin-left: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-weight: bold; color: #C00000; ">There was evidently more than one word missing, as the sense requires at least one of the three declined to tender</seg>
                     </p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>[for] the work, whereas smaller establishments have not the needful types. The hon. the Chief Secretary approved of the work being done in a private establishment; the letter [on] which Mr Grants approval is noted, has gone back to the C. S.'s office.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Ferd. von Mueller.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>5/5/82.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Will Mr Wilson kindly obtain or sign approval on the L2 form?</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">F.v.M.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn3" n="4">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">On 12 May 1882, the Chief Secretary, J. Grant, approved and initialled the memorandum and Wi</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">lson minuted: 'A/c. approved &amp; returned</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">'.</seg>
                     </p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
         </div>
